OL,5, Rising prices have driven some asylum  
OL,6, seekers to destitution, a charity has  
OL,7, warned.                                
OL,9,FThe Welsh Refugee Council (WRC) has    
OL,10,Fcalled for asylum seekers to be allowed
OL,11,Fto work in order to increase their     
OL,12,Fincome.                                
OL,14,FIt said it was having to support more  
OL,15,Fpeople with its hardship fund, as well 
OL,16,Fas clothes and food donations.         
OL,18,FThe Home Office said it provided       
OL,19,Faccommodation and a weekly allowance to
OL,20,Fsupport asylum seekers.                
